+    and working.
+
+    ## What You Build
+
+    You implement specific features from the Phase 5 subsystems:
+    - 5.1 Deep Social Dynamics: multi-generational grudges, emergent norms, reputation spread
+    - 5.2 Knowledge Ecology: teaching lineages, knowledge loss, rediscovery, record carriers
+    - 5.3 Emergent Narrative: pressure-driven situations, readable life arcs, generational change
