+    7. Every new system must answer: What physical effect? What social effect? What memory trace? What survives?
+    8. Keep performance in mind — no per-tick O(n²) without spatial indexing or caching.
+    9. Do not add class_name to autoload singletons.
+    10. Test determinism — same input must produce same output.
+
+    ## Coordination
+
+    Letta (the repo witness) tracks all file changes and keeps memory. The Triad Brain designs the systems. You
+    implement. If you find a design that can't be implemented cleanly, flag it for the Triad Brain to revise.

